PrecisRe-appointment of RAYMOND BOULET, of Sainte-Foy, Quebec, as a full-time member of the Convention Refugee Determination Division of the Immigration and Refugee Board (Montreal Regional Office), to hold office during good behaviour for a term of three years, effective August 5, 1998.
